{"tid":582650,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"（excel 大師請進）如何找excel 中最後一列的超連結","createTime":"2018-03-06T10:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T15:32:37.000Z","uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0bd0ac77009f724df36a19882a22c39697795aa5","tid":582650,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:59:11.000Z","msg":"想找excel 中最後列的超連結出來可如何做，例子<br />\n<br />\n        A              B                    C            D          E<br />\n<br />\n1  日期     Last version      1/3/18    2/3/18     3/3/18<br />\n<br />\n2 文件                                     ^                          ^<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n^是代表新版本的文件，同時己直接超連結了文件<br />\n<br />\n想問問如何將3/3/2018（即是E2)的^找到去last version 下（即是B2),同時又超連結到文件？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n救各位大師幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5130481f56063f59fc9aec5ec1955443a84ac2a7","tid":582650,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"竟然亂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n^是分最分別放在c2同e2個格"},{"pid":"65bf442783742fa8fbd436c2264f11e0ce0fa150","tid":582650,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/190535_bddfe7c88655962531aa9b64752ef1dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F190535_bddfe7c88655962531aa9b64752ef1dd.png&h=0f3e233a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自動找最後的超連結"},{"pid":"9d23d1efce661be4cd2830b9294b27985c66a347","tid":582650,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:48:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1912348662fddf59507f5781395b06e68c17b47","tid":582650,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:41:48.000Z"