2650,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T23:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/072827_1fe40f223c114b6904daf480fc891e9b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F072827_1fe40f223c114b6904daf480fc891e9b.png&h=62088af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文件實際有一千個，日期都有千個，還要日期不是連着，只有該日有文件更新先有新的日期創建<br />\n<br />\n我想找到每個文件最新的檔案到b2 column 中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:02:02.000Z","msg":"返大陸問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143379abc7a732ca4a4df0ca6bfb98b30286527c","tid":582650,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"=HYPERLINK(LOOKUP(2,1/(2:2&lt;&gt;&quot;&quot;),2:2))"},{"pid":"695e8836e47a684b53ffce68610de9a29f867a6b","tid":582650,"uid":122801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6365e478d83623daebb86523600190c4beb6ce5c","tid":582650,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"830c27c19a3914b753c1a79b87450b816182b0ae","tid":582650,"uid":122801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7b730b2165e0e1e89b912427adf0ba40dcd2e53","tid":582650,"uid":122801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T15:19:04.000Z","msg":"B1<br />\n=MAX(A5:A20)<br />\n<br />\nB2<br />\n=HYPERLINK(VLOOKUP(MAX(A6:A20),A6:B20,2,FALSE))"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T23:18:11.000Z","msg":"大師，我就是想要類似功效，找出一個文件的最新檔案，但我要做的不是只一個文件，那可以點整？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:32:37.000Z","msg":"唔熟， 唔知有無咩問題， 自己搵多D entry 測試下先好用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nB2<br />\n=HYPERLINK(INDEX(D2:I2,1,MATCH(MAX(IF(D2:I2&lt;&gt;&quot;&quot;,$D$1:$I$1)),$D$1:$I$1,0)))<br />\n<br />\n陣列公式黎，輸入完按 Ctrl+Shift+Enter <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/232429_4b8dee1e115d77a25cd2781ebc3579a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F232429_4b8dee1e115d77a25cd2781ebc3579a3.jpg&h=c0b0fed8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}